Maoriland
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:New Zealand, orig. journalistic or poetic, but later taken up by Sydney <i>Bulletin</i> writers and editors.
Origin: [none]
Register: informal
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes:
